title: Iswra onkhang baobai
lyrics:
Iswra onkhang baobai -2
“Gwdan bwswr jwngnw hwbai
Fwrbukhou hambai bwnw”-2
(A)
Rongja-mini mwsani de 
Dinwi gwdan bwthwrao
Pap mani khou garnanwi
 Fwidw dhwrwm lamayao-2

“Bese somaina be san hatorkhi
Khwlw-Khwlw bar gwjwn sudem”-2
(B)
Gwdan gwsw lananwi 
Phwrbu khou jwng sibigwn
Nwngni guar gangkhongao
Gojobdw jwng boikhoubw

“Bese somaina be san hatorkhi
Khwlw-Khwlw bar gwjwn sudem”-2
